---
title: Homestyle Meatloaf with Roasted Root Vegetables and Thyme Gravy
description: It might not be your mom’s recipe, but we promise this homey dish will bring back memories. Flavored with mild shallot and woodsy thyme, our meatloaf packs sophisticated flavor and serious tenderness. Of course, the dish wouldn’t be complete without a generous smothering of homemade gravy.
